06daba80b27a9aec46c3c4331a353725e7cb6beb.query:
UPDATE
                    tasks
                SET
                    completed_at = CASE
                        WHEN $2 THEN CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'UTC'
                        ELSE NULL
                    END
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    completed_at

09e3c3722e1c3db95e9a201f8177d3d648701c99.query:
SELECT
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at,
                    start_date,
                    end_date
                FROM
                    tasks

0a38a4263db5e25680c5a7280cc1405c5af305f3.query:
DELETE FROM
                    tasks
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId"

2f785d542606974133cda3d43029bbaf096240f3.query:
INSERT INTO tasks (
                    title,
                    start_date,
                    end_date
                )
                VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3
                )
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at,
                    start_date,
                    end_date

8cddfd2c48d6f46461a68c41a1c3225b415d1794.query:
UPDATE
                    tasks
                SET
                    title = $2,
                    start_date = $3,
                    end_date = $4
                WHERE
                    id = $1
                RETURNING
                    id as "id: TaskId",
                    title,
                    completed_at,
                    start_date,
                    end_date
